{
  "title": "ReFi Roundup #46: A Regen Christmas & The REC Renaissance 🎄⚡️",
  "slug": "refi-roundup-46",
  "html": "<p><em>Hey everyone, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ThoughtFloats\">ThoughtFloats</a> from the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ThoughtFloats\">ReFi Weekly Rewind</a> and <a href=\"https://web3climate.substack.com/\">Venturing in ReFi</a> here with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MontyMerlin\">Monty Bryant</a> bringing you another Roundup to round out the year! Let's jump right in!</em></p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/2022-ReFi-Holiday-Gift-Guide.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/2022-ReFi-Holiday-Gift-Guide.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/2022-ReFi-Holiday-Gift-Guide.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h1 id=\"happy-holidays-regens-%F0%9F%8E%84%E2%98%83%EF%B8%8F\">Happy Holidays Regens! 🎄☃️</h1><p>The new year is just two weeks away and the holiday season is in full swing.  Like the good ecologically-and-socially-conscious warrior you are, you’ve spent the year building toward a regenerative future we all wish to realize.  But with all that work, you might not yet have finalized your gift list for the rapidly approaching season of giving. So whether your looking for the perfect gift for your regenerative friends, or if you are wanting to serve up some green pills to the unconverted, we've got you covered with this <strong>Regen Holiday Gift Guide 2022</strong>! 🎁</p><h3 id=\"gift-idea-1-carbon-%F0%9F%8C%90\">Gift Idea #1:  Carbon 🌐</h3><p>The ReFi community has worked super hard all year. As a result, we now have the tools to make it incredibly easy to give the gift of on-chain carbon offsets! Here are some available resources to help you retire wisely:</p><ul><li><strong><a href=\"https://app.toucan.earth/pools?chainId=\">Toucan Protocol - </a></strong><a href=\"https://app.toucan.earth/pools?chainId=\">Toucan dApp</a> (with step <strong><a href=\"https://blog.toucan.earth/carbon-retirement-christmas/\">this step-by-step guide</a></strong> on how gift carbon) 🐧</li><li><strong><a href=\"https://offsetra.com/buy/by-the-tonne\">Offsetra</a></strong><a href=\"https://offsetra.com/buy/by-the-tonne\"> - “Offset by the tonne”</a> with verified proof-of-retirement 🧾</li><li><strong><a href=\"https://www.loveletter.klimadao.finance/\">KlimaDAO</a></strong><a href=\"https://www.loveletter.klimadao.finance/\"> - Love Letters</a> dedicate retirements to a person or cause 💚</li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://blog.toucan.earth/carbon-retirement-christmas/\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-17.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-17.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/12/image-17.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-17.png 1500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption><a href=\"https://blog.toucan.earth/carbon-retirement-christmas/\">A gift for the planet &amp; people in your life</a></figcaption></figure><p>You can also purchase credits from specific projects on <a href=\"https://app.regen.network/\">Regen Market</a>, <a href=\"https://www.senken.io/projects\">Senken</a>, &amp; <a href=\"https://nori.com/remove-carbon\">Nori</a>.  There are so many more on-chain carbon credit marketplaces set to launch in 2023, so we’re already looking forward to next year’s list!</p><h3 id=\"gift-idea-2-social-and-environmental-impact-%F0%9F%A4%9D\">Gift Idea #2:  Social and Environmental Impact 🤝</h3><p>Beyond carbon, you can dedicate verifiable social or environmental impact to your friends and family.  Check out these amazing Web3-powered options:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://app.impactmarket.com/\"><strong>Impact Market</strong></a> - donate to social causes and provide support for vulnerable communities around the world 🤲</li><li><strong><a href=\"https://nft.moss.earth/\">Moss.Earth NFTs</a></strong> - gift a digitally-monitored portion of rainforest preservation 🎋</li><li><strong><a href=\"https://doingud.com/\">DoinGUD NFT Marketplace</a></strong> - purchase impact-driven NFTs ☄️</li><li><strong><a href=\"https://app.angryteenagers.xyz/pick-impact\">Angry Teenagers NFT</a></strong> - plant trees and make a difference 🌱</li><li><strong><a href=\"https://refigratitude.xyz/\">ReFiGratitude.xyz</a></strong> - gift an NFT, retire carbon, and support black artists all at the same time! 💯</li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://refigratitude.xyz/\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/Screenshot-2022-12-16-at-11.14.19-am.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1588\" height=\"838\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/Screenshot-2022-12-16-at-11.14.19-am.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/12/Screenshot-2022-12-16-at-11.14.19-am.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/Screenshot-2022-12-16-at-11.14.19-am.png 1588w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption><a href=\"https://refigratitude.xyz/\">ReFi Gratitude - Launching today!</a></figcaption></figure><p>There are many more ReFi NFTs and ways to verify impact on-chain, these are just a few suggestions to get your gift-giving mind flowing.</p><h3 id=\"gift-idea-3-regen-reading-%F0%9F%93%9A\">Gift Idea #3:  Regen Reading 📚</h3><p>Knowledge is one of the best gifts out there and can also be a leverage point for positive climate action. + if you want to spare the printed paper and shipping, gifting digital books is easy.  For Kindle users, Amazon has a simple <a href=\"https://kdp.amazon.com/en_US/help/topic/G200652260\">“Buy for others”</a> button, making it easy to gift digital books.  Here is a (heavily abridged) Regen Reading List including some of our favorite titles to give you ideas:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Sacred-Economics-Revised-Society-Transition-ebook/dp/B088QLDG23/\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/Sacred-Economics-Charles-Eisenstein-Buy.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/Sacred-Economics-Charles-Eisenstein-Buy.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/Sacred-Economics-Charles-Eisenstein-Buy.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Sacred-Economics-Revised-Society-Transition-ebook/dp/B088QLDG23/\"><strong>Sacred Economics</strong></a> by Charles Eisenstein</li><li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Speed-Scale-Action-Solving-Climate-ebook/dp/B0962VSKW2/\"><strong>Speed and Scale</strong></a> by John Doerr and Ryan Panchadsaram</li><li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Regeneration-Ending-Climate-Crisis-Generation-ebook/dp/B0915J14GG/\"><strong>Regeneration</strong></a> by Paul Hawken</li><li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Doughnut-Economics-Seven-21st-Century-Economist-ebook/dp/B06X9C63SX/\"><strong>Donut Economics</strong></a> by Kate Raworth</li><li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Braiding-Sweetgrass-Indigenous-Scientific-Knowledge-ebook/dp/B00D0V44LC/\"><strong>Braiding Sweetgrass</strong></a> by Robin Wall Kimmerer</li><li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Regenerative-Enterprise-Optimizing-Multi-capital-Abundance-ebook/dp/B08L1G5VFP/\"><strong>Regenerative Enterprise</strong></a> by Ethan Roland and Gregory Landua</li><li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Uninhabitable-Earth-Life-After-Warming-ebook/dp/B07GVPFH5V/\"><strong>The Uninhabitable Earth</strong></a> by David Wallace Wells</li><li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Voluntary-Carbon-Markets-International-Environmental-ebook/dp/B0084CM53G/\"><strong>Voluntary Carbon Markets</strong></a> by Ricardo Bayon, Amanda Hawn, and Katherine Hamilton</li><li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Ministry-Future-Kim-Stanley-Robinson-ebook/dp/B084FY1NXB/\"><strong>The Ministry for the Future: A Novel</strong></a> by Kim Stanley Robinson</li><li><a href=\"https://store.gitcoin.co/products/green-pill-book-digital-edition\"><strong>Green Pill Book</strong></a> By Gitcoin Founder Kevin Owocki.</li><li><a href=\"https://www.google.co.uk/books/edition/The_Blue_Commons/03WMEAAAQBAJ?hl=en\"><strong>The Blue Commons</strong></a> Rescuing the Economy of the Sea By Guy Standing</li><li><a href=\"https://www.google.co.uk/books/edition/The_Intersectional_Environmentalist/uIY1EAAAQBAJ?hl=en\"><strong>The Intersectional Environmentalist</strong></a> by Leah Thomas</li><li><strong><a href=\"https://www.google.co.uk/books/edition/Regenesis/gcGOEAAAQBAJ?hl=en\">Regenesis</a> </strong>Feeding the World Without Devouring the Planet By George Monbiot</li><li><a href=\"https://www.penguin.co.uk/books/446610/the-climate-book-by-thunberg-greta/9780241547472\"><strong>The Climate Book</strong></a> by Greta Thunberg<br></li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-18.png\" width=\"1500\" height=\"2250\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-18.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/12/image-18.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-18.png 1500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-21.png\" width=\"1650\" height=\"2550\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-21.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/12/image-21.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/12/image-21.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-21.png 1650w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-22.png\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-22.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/12/image-22.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/12/image-22.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-22.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-20.png\" width=\"1674\" height=\"2560\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-20.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/12/image-20.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/12/image-20.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-20.png 1674w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-23.png\" width=\"1200\" height=\"845\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-23.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/12/image-23.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-23.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-25.png\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-25.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/12/image-25.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/12/image-25.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-25.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-24.png\" width=\"1536\" height=\"2048\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-24.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/12/image-24.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-24.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div></figure><h3 id=\"gift-idea-4-gitcoin-shop-%F0%9F%A4%96\">Gift Idea #4:  Gitcoin Shop! 🤖</h3><p>Theres a bunch of cool ReFi related gifts available at the awesome <a href=\"https://store.gitcoin.co/\">Gitcoin Schwag Store</a>. Some of my favourites below 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide kg-card-hascaption\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-26.png\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-26.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/12/image-26.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/12/image-26.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-26.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-27.png\" width=\"858\" height=\"1200\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-27.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-27.png 858w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div><figcaption><a href=\"https://pluriverse.wtf/\">pluriverse.wtf</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://store.gitcoin.co/collections/posters/products/coordination-mechanisms-poster\">Coordination Mechanisms Poster</a></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">gm<br><br>happy almost holidays y&#39;all! <a href=\"https://t.co/YlNtlZK3tt\">pic.twitter.com/YlNtlZK3tt</a></p>&mdash; 🦋 Ben WΞst 🐒 🌻 @benwest@denizens.social (@BenWest) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BenWest/status/1602699936222543873?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 13, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>Remember, it’s the season for <a href=\"https://giveth.io/\">giving</a>!  Give freely to others, to yourself, to humanity, and to the earth.  Take time to recharge, give thanks, and we’ll see you in 2023 for more regeneration!</p><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2022/11/ReFi-Cover-2.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2022/11/ReFi-Cover-2.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-podcasts-%F0%9F%8E%99%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi Podcasts 🎙️</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emtop-audio-and-video-content-from-creators-across-the-web-em%F0%9F%98%8A\"><em>Top audio and video content from creators across the web </em>😊</h3></div><h3 id=\"recs-renaissance-with-arkreen-jasmine-energy-and-reneum-institute-refi-podcast-s2e20-%E2%AD%95%EF%B8%8F\">RECs Renaissance with Arkreen, Jasmine Energy, and Reneum Institute | <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A7MiGu_q3-s\">ReFi Podcast S2E20</a> ⭕️</h3><p>In this episode, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto\">John Ellison</a> discussed the importance of Renewable Energy Credits (RECs) as a new asset in the ReFi space with pioneers from 3 leading REC-focused ReFi Projects: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TDaltonC\">T. Dalton Combs</a> of <a href=\"https://www.jasmine.energy/\">Jasmine Energy</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/briannaleewelsh\">Brianna Welsh</a> of <a href=\"https://reneum.com/\">Reneum Institute</a>, and Carl Weaver from <a href=\"https://www.arkreen.com/\">Arkreen Network</a>.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/A7MiGu_q3-s?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"ReFi S2E20: RECs Renaissance with Arkreen, Jasmine Energy &amp; Reneum Institute\"></iframe></figure><p>Read the <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/recs-renaissance-w-reneum/\">deep dive</a>, <a href=\"https://anchor.fm/refipodcast/episodes/RECs-Renaissance-with-Arkreen--Jasmine-Energy--Reneum-Institute-e1s65gc\">listen</a> on your podcasting favorite platform, or check out the <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A7MiGu_q3-s\">episode on Youtube</a>. </p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://anchor.fm/refipodcast/episodes/RECs-Renaissance-with-Arkreen--Jasmine-Energy--Reneum-Institute-e1s65gc\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Listen to the episode</a></div><h2 id=\"other-%F0%9F%94%A5-podcasts-on-our-radar\">Other 🔥 Podcasts on our Radar:</h2><ul><li><strong>All About Impact DAOs: </strong><a href=\"https://www.buzzsprout.com/2057401/11847815\">featuring Wasabi of <strong>Kokonut Network</strong></a> on Agriculture DAOs as the next big ReFi opportunity.</li><li><strong>Crypto Altruism Podcast: </strong><a href=\"https://www.cryptoaltruism.org/blog/crypto-altruism-podcast-episode82-desciworld-science-as-it-should-be\">featuring Joshua Bates and Jelani Clarke of <strong>Desci World</strong></a> to discuss how Decentralized Science (DeSci) can build a world where scientific research and progress is unrestricted, unbiased, and uncensorable.</li><li><strong>This Week In ReFi: </strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9s57ASJoHUc\">Episode 26 <strong>Dynamic Pooling</strong></a> where hosts Slaptain Shwirv and Rez discuss recent ReFi news &amp; updates including a deep dive on Thallo’s concept of <a href=\"https://www.thallo.io/dynamic-pooling/\">Carbon Credit Dynamic Pooling</a>.</li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9s57ASJoHUc?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"Dynamic Pooling - This Week In Refi - Episode 26\"></iframe></figure><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-dark\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-newsbites-%F0%9F%97%9E%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi NewsBites 🗞️</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emthe-latest-updates-across-refi-twitter-and-beyondem\"><em>The latest updates across ReFi Twitter and beyond...</em></h3></div><h3 id=\"refigratitude-collection-details-%F0%9F%99%8F\"><strong>#ReFiGratitude Collection Details</strong> 🙏</h3><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/btruax\">Brian Truax</a> of <a href=\"https://loalabs.io/\">LOA Labs</a> dropped a link to the full <a href=\"https://refigratitude.xyz/\">ReFiGratitude</a> NFT project explainer, including how the mint works, details on the collection &amp; gifting experience, and more.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Ok, I got you fam. Check out this Notion for the details:<br><br>👉How does <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFiGratitude?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFiGratitude</a> work<br>👉Details of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NFT?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NFT</a> Collection<br>👉How to Gift the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NFTs?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NFTs</a><br><br>I can improve this tomorrow when the mint experience is live.<a href=\"https://t.co/FJnSo6UcYG\">https://t.co/FJnSo6UcYG</a><br><br>Let me know if you have any Qs!</p>&mdash; Brian Truax (🌳,🌳) (@btruax) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/btruax/status/1601783273344372738?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 11, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p><strong>“The Definitive Guide to Impact DAOs” </strong><br><a href=\"https://twitter.com/MontyMerlin\">Monty Bryant</a> shared a new book by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/deeparocks\">Deepa</a> of <a href=\"https://impactdaos.xyz/\">Impact DAO</a> Media.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">What is an <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ImpactDAO?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ImpactDAO</a>? What are they good for? Should you join one?<br><br>Whether you are a complete newbie, or a seasoned Web3 builder, the amazing <a href=\"https://twitter.com/deeparocks?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@DeepaRocks</a> from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/impactdaos?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ImpactDAOs</a> Media has you covered with her new book!<a href=\"https://t.co/Gs9GUOn6j5\">https://t.co/Gs9GUOn6j5</a></p>&mdash; Monty (🧙) Bryant (🌴,🌴) (@MontyMerlin) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MontyMerlin/status/1603082912647233536?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 14, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"also-on-our-radar-this-week\">Also on our radar this week</h3><ul><li>🦸‍♀️ <strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/Givethio/status/1602705396946423813\">Giveth launched GIVpower</a>, </strong>allowing participants in the Giveth ecosystem to boost support for the public goods projects they choose.</li><li>🎁 <strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ToucanProtocol/status/1602718148125335552\">Toucan Recapped the Year</a> </strong>and showed you how to give the gift of carbon this Christmas.</li><li>📺 <strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0zECztpGLbM\">CBC Vancouver featured ReFi</a>.</strong> A segment on the environmental challenges of the metaverse with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/josephpallant\">Joseph Pallant</a> of <a href=\"https://www.blockchainforclimate.org/\">Blockchain for Climate Foundation</a>.</li><li>💚 <strong><a href=\"https://grant-explorer.gitcoin.co/#/round/1/0xdf75054cd67217aee44b4f9e4eb